253
00:17:10,190 --> 00:17:12,960
Maafkan aku. Tiba-tiba aku merusak suasana.

254
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:15,859
Pak Oh.

255
00:17:16,389 --> 00:17:19,100
Ibumu akan sangat bahagia.

256
00:17:19,260 --> 00:17:21,530
Karena kamu menjadi guru yang hebat.

257
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:24,939
Benarkah?

258
00:17:24,939 --> 00:17:26,070
Tentu saja.

259
00:17:26,899 --> 00:17:30,139
