304
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:49,510
Mengatakan sesuatu?

305
00:19:50,109 --> 00:19:51,649
Aku hanya merasa haus.

306
00:19:52,250 --> 00:19:53,350
Ambillah air putih.

307
00:19:54,219 --> 00:19:56,889
Jika unggahan tentang putra si tikus itu benar,

308
00:19:56,889 --> 00:19:59,619
kuharap dia dipermalukan untuk selamanya.

309
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:16,310
Soo Bin.

